Definition: cause to become stonelike or stiff or dazed and stunned from fright
Example: The horror petrified his feelings; Fear petrified her thinking
Synonyms: deaden, cause, to, become, stonelike, or, stiff, dazed, and, stunned, from, fright, The, horror, petrified, his, feelings, Fear, her, thinking
Frame: 11
Category: verb.change
